data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home in Sevier county is within minutes of shopping, Dollywood ,restaurants, and many more attractions ,but sits on the outskirts away from all the hustle and bustle, and with views of the Smoky Mountains. The tin roof on the house is less than a year old and the solar panels on the roof help save on your electric bill. The house also has a cozy rock fireplace in the den for cold winter nights. Full camper hookup with 50 amp service. This house is a must see.
